<item>
            <title>[PIG-1749] Update Pig parser so that function arguments can contain newline characters</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-1749</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We want to add this feature so that users can put long function argument strings in multiple lines. &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-1748&quot; title=&quot;Add load/store function AvroStorage for avro data&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-1748&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-1748&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; depends on this. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12480860">PIG-1749</key>
            <summary>Update Pig parser so that function arguments can contain newline characters</summary>
